{"tid":2207160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯前顧問表態支持拜登　批評特朗普抗疫不力","createTime":"2020-09-18T03:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T04:05:42.000Z","uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8588f9ed71da971d976eb4675add677febb836","tid":2207160,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"彭斯的前國土安全顧問兼白宮抗疫小組成員特羅伊（Olivia Troye）透過「反對特朗普的共和黨選民」（Republican Voters Against Trump）發表短片，形容為特朗普工作是「恐怖」，她指對方只顧自己的連任機會多於帶領國家抗疫，批評特朗普只顧自己。<br />\n<br />\n特羅伊提到，特朗普曾經在白宮抗疫小組的一次會議上表示，病毒或是一件好事，稱自己不喜歡與其他人握手，因此無須與這些醜惡的人握手。她指「這些醜惡的人」正是特朗普口中一直關心的人，而他們至今仍然出席對方的集會。<br />\n<br />\n她認為如果特朗普認真看待疫情，或向民眾警告疫情的嚴重性，他或可以減慢病毒散播速度，拯救生命。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RVAT2020/status/1306685541220524046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRVAT2020%2Fstatus%2F1306685541220524046&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=234aef62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRVAT2020%2Fstatus%2F1306685541220524046&h=9f17a859\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RVAT2020/status/1306685541220524046</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2020/09/17/olivia-troye-ad-trump-coronavirus-417428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F09%2F17%2Folivia-troye-ad-trump-coronavirus-417428&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=dc82a198\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/news/2020/09/17/olivia-troye-ad-trump-coronavirus-417428</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n川皇必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e734ca28e600159b61397bce4c6fea94945e0b2","tid":2207160,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"Dem 咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i